_ignoreDrag

boolean _ignoreDrag
this variable is set to avoid a wired behavior in selecting an element by clicking. If you click an element, the element is then selected. If you keep the cursor in the same location and try to press the button and drag the element, the drag process wouldn't happen since this LayoutSelect tool is till the active component that captured the mouse event eventhough after an element is selected, this tool has been set backward to the element's drag&resize frame. If you just move the mouse little bit, it will work perfectly. So to avoid the wired behavior, I added this additional variable so that when the mouse pressed point is the same as previous one, the drag process will be ignored.
